  "text": "The BTA technique may enable formation of biologic width in three dimensions (Fig. 10) . The reasons for this favorable outcome are similar to those for platform switching, in which an implant abutment with a diameter smaller than that of the implant fixture is used to create a functional implant-bone distance, which counteracts bone resorption and gingival recession [CITATION_1] .",
